# IMPORT PRESCRIPTIONS 2.0 – AI PRESCRIPTION INTAKE & CLINICAL ORDER ORCHESTRATION CENTER

## Objective

Transform this page from a simple prescription uploader into a complete clinical intake workflow.

The goal is not only to upload prescriptions.

The goal is to:

- Extract prescriptions automatically
- Identify patients
- Identify physicians
- Match prescribed products with Atlas catalog
- Detect unavailable products
- Suggest therapeutic alternatives
- Generate quotations
- Generate compounding requests
- Create orders automatically
- Validate regulatory restrictions
- Create treatment protocols
- Synchronize with CRM and Patient Records

The experience must be optimized for both desktop and mobile.

